data.title: Christine Rodd
data.meta_description: Christine Rodd is a Cisgender Homosexual character played by Trudy Hellier on Neighbours - Clich√©s: Parent
data.text: Following the breakdown of her marriage to Allan Steiger, Christine realises that she is gay and she struggles to tell her ex-husband or their daughter, Pepper. It becomes even more difficult for her, when her sister takes the news badly. Christine becomes the head mechanic at Carpenter's Mechanics and begins working with Janae Timmins, whom she does not get on with.
